      </div>
      <br />
      <div class="profile">
        <div class="profileimage">
          <Image
            src={alpannImage}
            alt="alpanimage"
            style="width: 100px; height: 100px; border-radius: 50%; float: left; display: block; margin: 0 auto;"
          />
        </div>
        <div class="profiletext">
          I am a student in the Informatics Engineering Study Program at
          Pamulang University. I am currently learning in the world of web
          development, especially in the field of front-end development.
        </div>
      </div>

      <p>
        <div class="container">
          <div class="gambar">
            <Image
              src={alpannnnnnnImage}
              alt="foto 1"
              style="width: 100px; height: 100px;  float: center;"
            />
          </div>
          <div class="gambar">
            <Image
              src={alpannnnImage}
              alt="foto 2"
              style="width: 100px; height: 100px; float: center;"
            />
          </div>
          <div class="gambar">
            <Image
              src={alpannnnnnImage}
              alt="foto 3"
              style="width: 100px; height: 100px; float: center;"
            />
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="container">
          <div class="gambar">
            <Image
              src={alpannnnnImage}
              alt="foto 4"
              style="width: 100px; height: 100px; float: center;"
            />
          </div>
          <div class="gambar">
            <Image
              src={alpannnnnnnnImage}
              alt="foto 5"
              style="width: 100px; height: 100px; float: center;"
            />
          </div>
          <div class="gambar">
            <Image
              src={gitarImage}
              alt="foto 6"
              style="width: 100px; height: 100px; float: center;"
            />
          </div>
        </div>
        <br />
        <strong>Contact me via</strong>
        <br />
        <a class="featured">
          <div class="contact-container">
            <a href="https://www.instagram.com/kelraskie/" target="_blank">
              <Image
                src={instagramImage}
                alt="instagram image"
                style="width: 40px; height: 40px; float: center; margin-right: 20px;"
              />
            </a>
            <span class="username">@kelraskie</span>
          </div>
          <div class="contact-container">
            <a
              href="https://mail.google.com/?alfanhidayat12321@gmail.comm"
              target="_blank"
            >
              <Image
                src={emailImage}
                alt="email image"
                style="width: 40px; height: 40px; float: center; margin-right: 20px;"
              />
            </a>
            <span class="username">alfanhidayat12321@gmail.com</span>
          </div>
        </a>
        You can contact me via email & instagram, or <strong
          >click image.</strong
        >
        <div class="wrapper">
          <ul class="dynamic-text">
            <li><span>Thank Youu!ðŸ‘‹â€Žâ€Ž</span></li>
          </ul>
        </div>
        <style>
          .container {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: center;
            align-items: center;
            width: 100%;
            height: 100%;
          }

          .gambar {
            background-color: #f8f9fa;
            border: 1px solid #dee2e6;
            border-radius: 0.25rem;
            padding: 10px;
            box-shadow: 0 2px 4px rgba(190, 88, 88, 0.1);
          }

          .gambar img {
            width: 100%;
            height: auto;
            margin: 0 auto;
          }
          .contact-container {
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
          }

          .instagram-icon {
            width: 24px;
            height: 24px;
            margin-right: 8px;
          }

          .keterampilann {
            text-align: left;
            color: black;
            font-size: 18px;
          }
          .username {
            margin-top: -4px;
            font-size: 18px;
            color: black;
          }
          .wrapper {
            display: flex;
          }

          .wrapper .text {
            color: black;
            font-size: 25px;
            font-weight: 700;
            margin-top: 40px;
          }
          .wrapper .dynamic-text {
            margin-left: -39px;
            height: 90px;
            line-height: 90px;
            overflow: hidden;
          }

          .dynamic-text li {
            list-style: none;
            color: black;
            font-size: 20px;
            font-weight: 500;
            position: relative;
            top: 0;
            animation: slide 12 steps(4) infinite;
          }

          @keyframes slide {
            100% {
              top: -360px;
            }
          }

          .dynamic-text li span {
            position: relative;
            margin: 5px o;
            line-height: 90px;
          }
          .dynamic-text li span::after {
            content: "";
            position: absolute;
            left: 0;
            height: 78px;
            width: 100%;
            background: white;
            border-left: 2px solid white;
            animation: typingg 3s steps(14) infinite;
          }

          @keyframes typingg {
            40%,
            60% {
              left: calc(100% + 30px);
            }
            100% {
              left: 0;
            }
          }

          .profile {
            color: black;
            text-align: right;
            margin-bottom: 2rem;
            border: 1px solid rgba(var(--accent-light), 25%);
            background: linear-gradient(
              rgba(var(--accent-dark), 66%),
              rgba(var(--accent-dark), 33%)
            );
            padding: 1.5rem;
            border-radius: 8px;
            font-size: 18px;
            border: 1px solid black;
            background: white;
          }

          .gambar img {
            width: 100%;
            height: auto;
            margin: 0 auto;
            transition: transform 0.3s ease-in-out;
          }

          .gambar:hover img {
            transform: scale(1.5);
          }

          .typing-text {
            overflow: hidden;
            border-right: 0.15em solid black;
            white-space: nowrap;
            font-size: 20px;
            width: 41%;
            animation:
              infinite typing 10s forwards,
              blink-border 1s infinite step-start;
          }

          @keyframes typing {
            0%,
            100% {
              width: 0;
            }
            50% {
              width: 41%;
            }
          }

          @keyframes closing {
            0%,
            100% {
              width: 41%;
            }
            50% {
              width: 0;
            }
          }

          @keyframes blink-border {
            50% {
              border-color: transparent;
            }
          }
        </style>
      </p>
    </main>
    <Footer />
  </body>
</html>
